wikipedia_page.main: Alison Edith Debenham, later Alison Edith Le Plat, (1903-1967) was a British painter and artist.

response: On 8 November 1892 he married Cicely Kenrick (1869–1950), daughter of William Kenrick.  The couple had eight children, including the artist Alison Debenham.
